column1: /bin/sh -c ARCH= && dpkgArch="$(dpkg --print-architecture)" &&     case "${dpkgArch##*-}" in       amd64) ARCH='amd64'
column12: esac &&     wget --no-verbose https://dl.influxdata.com/influxdb/releases/influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb.asc &&     wget --no-verbose https://dl.influxdata.com/influxdb/releases/influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb &&     gpg --batch --verify influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb.asc influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb &&     dpkg -i influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb &&     rm -f influxdb_${INFLUXDB_VERSION}_${ARCH}.deb*

column4: do         gpg --keyserver ha.pool.sks-keyservers.net --recv-keys "$key" ||         gpg --keyserver pgp.mit.edu --recv-keys "$key" ||         gpg --keyserver keyserver.pgp.com --recv-keys "$key"

column3: apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends   apt-transport-https   ca-certificates   curl   netbase   wget
